    <briefdescription>
<para>Static singleton for CAN sub-node (<ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref>) firmware. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Manages MCP23017 expander registration and cache, <ref refid="classADS1115" kindref="compound">ADS1115</ref> registration, the 8-step boot sequence, per-loop interrupt dispatch and polling fallback, CAN EVT batching, CTRL_BCAST dispatch, SYNC_REQ response, and the 500 ms HB_n heartbeat. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
